5	Privacy Policy - Outlet		1	<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>Privacy Policy/ Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C </strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>This policy is effective as of March 1, 2024</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Introduction</strong></p>\r\n<p>This Privacy Notice elucidates how Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C and its affiliated companies utilize your information. It applies to all users of our websites and platforms, encompassing mobile applications, electronic services, social networking sites, interactive features, and online services. If you engage with our services ("Service"), kindly review the Terms of Use governing your Service usage. By using the Service, you affirm that you have perused and comprehended this Privacy Notice. If you disagree with this Privacy Notice, please refrain from providing us with your information or utilizing the Service.</p>\r\n<p>We retain the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. In the event of significant changes, we will apprise you via email (dispatched to the email address in your account) or through a notice on the Service before the modification takes effect. The "Effective Date" above denotes the last revision date for this Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n<p>At Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C, we hold the privacy of our website visitors in high regard. This Privacy Policy delineates the types of information Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C collects and records, along with its utilization.</p>\r\n<p>For any queries about our Privacy Policy or if you need further clarification, please don't hesitate to get in touch with us at&nbsp;<a title="info@dealsdrive.app" href="mailto:info@dealsdrive.app">info@dealsdrive.app</a></p>\r\n<p>Kindly note that this policy pertains exclusively to our online activities and is relevant solely to information shared and collected on Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C 's website. It does not extend to information collected through other channels.</p>\r\n<p>Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C, its subsidiaries, and affiliates globally (referred to collectively as "Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C," "Company," "we," or "our") recognize the significance of protecting privacy for all users ("you") who visit and utilize our websites. This includes registered users or guests and encompasses any content, functionality, and services provided on or through our websites, webpages, and mobile applications designed for dedicated non-browser-based interaction on smartphones, tablets, and other devices ("Sites").</p>\r\n<p>This Privacy Policy elucidates our rationale for collecting and processing your personal information, as well as our practices for collecting, using, maintaining, retaining, protecting, and disclosing your personal data when you visit any of our Sites, irrespective of your location. Additionally, it apprises you of your privacy rights and the legal safeguards protecting these rights.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Consent</strong></h2>\r\n<h4><strong>1. Types of Information</strong></h4>\r\n<p>We Collect Personal data, or information that can identify an individual, is encompassed within this term. It excludes data where the identity has been removed, rendering it anonymous. Depending on the products/services you use and your interactions with our Sites, we collect various types of information from or about you. This includes, but is not limited to, the following categories of personal data:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Identity Data: Includes first name, last name, address, username, marital status, title, age group, and gender.</li>\r\n<li>Contact Data: Encompasses billing address, delivery address, location, email address, and/or telephone numbers.</li>\r\n<li>Financial Data: Comprises payment card details and payment history.</li>\r\n<li>Transaction Data: Involves details about payments to and from you, as well as information about products and services purchased.</li>\r\n<li>Technical Data: Encompasses IP address, login data, browser type and version, device details, operating system, hardware version, platform, file and software names, device identifiers, time zone settings, and location.</li>\r\n<li>Profile Data: Includes your username and password, purchases, interests, preferences, feedback, and survey responses.</li>\r\n<li>Usage Data: Encompasses information about how you use our Sites, products, and services, including the redemption of offers and device usage patterns.</li>\r\n<li>Other Data: Encompasses photos or data uploaded to our Sites, communications with us via various channels, third-party partner information, and networks and connections available to us.</li>\r\n<li>Marketing and Communications Data: Encompasses your preferences in receiving marketing and your communication preferences.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>We also collect, use, and share aggregated data, such as statistical or demographic data, for various purposes. Aggregated Data, derived from personal data but not considered personal data in law, may be used for statistical analysis. If aggregated data is combined with personal data to identify you directly or indirectly, it is treated as personal data in accordance with this Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n<p>We do not collect Special Categories of Personal Data, such as philosophical beliefs, sex life, sexual orientation, political opinions, trade union membership, health information, genetic and biometric data, criminal convictions, or offenses.</p>\r\n<p>Types of Information We Collect&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We may collect the following categories of personal information:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Identifiers: Such as names, addresses, email addresses, telephone numbers, or other communication addresses.</li>\r\n<li>Demographic Information: Including age group, birthdate, and gender.</li>\r\n<li>Commercial Information: Relevant to lifestyle, interests, activities, purchasing tendencies, and order history.</li>\r\n<li>Location Information: Including country, city, or neighborhood, and more specific location information provided through GPS functionality.</li>\r\n<li>Financial Information: Collected for processing payments, encompassing payment card details.</li>\r\n<li>Internet and Network Activity Information: Covering browsing behavior, search history, and interactions with websites and advertisements.</li>\r\n<li>Inferences Regarding Preferences: Assessments of products or services of interest.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The personal information you are asked to provide and the reasons for providing it will be transparent at the point of collection. If you contact us directly, we may receive additional information, such as your name, email address, phone number, message content, and attachments. During account registration, we may request contact information, including name, company name, address, email address, and telephone number.</p>\r\n<h3>FAILURE TO PROVIDE PERSONAL DATA</h3>\r\n<p>If personal data is required by law or under a contract, and you fail to provide it when requested, we may be unable to perform the contract or fulfill your requests.</p>\r\n<h4>2. How Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C Gathers Information Information Collection from Various Sources:</h4>\r\n<p><strong>1. Direct Submission:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Information provided by you during Service usage, purchases, registration, or interaction.</li>\r\n<li>Voluntarily entered information in postings, comments, or forums within the Service.</li>\r\n<li>Collected details from emails, including your email address and content.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>2. Device Information:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Collected details about the devices used to access the Service, such as hardware model, operating system, IP address, and device interaction.</li>\r\n<li>Information on access times, browser types, and language through the use of cookies, web beacons, and similar technologies.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>3. Location Information:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Collection of location information, including general details associated with your IP address and specific information from GPS functionality (if agreed).</li>\r\n<li>Utilization of location data to customize the Service, potentially shared with affiliates, agents, vendors, or advertisers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>4. Third-Party Sources:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Obtaining information from third-party sources like vendors, web hosting providers, analytics providers, or advertisers.</li>\r\n<li>Accessing information from third-party services with your permission, such as social media networks</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Methods of Data Collection:</h4>\r\n<p><strong>1. Direct Interactions:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Provision of Identity, Contact, and Financial Data through forms, correspondence, purchases, account creation, subscriptions, requests, competitions, or surveys.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2. Automated Technologies or Interactions:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Automatic collection of Technical Data through cookies, server logs, web beacons, and similar technologies.</p>\r\n<p>Categorized cookies for various purposes: strictly necessary, performance, functionality, and targeting/advertising.</p>\r\n<p><strong>3. Third Parties or Publicly Available Sources:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Receipt of personal data from third parties such as analytics providers, advertising networks, search information providers, and contracted third parties.</p>\r\n<p>Reception of Contact, Financial, and Transaction Data from providers of technical, payment, and delivery services.</p>\r\n<p>Collection of Identity and Contact Data from data brokers or aggregators and publicly available sources. Note: Personal information collected automatically may be linked to information obtained from other sources or provided by you</p>\r\n<p><strong>3. How Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C Utilizes and Use Your Information</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Utilization and use of Collected Information:</strong>&nbsp;We employ the information gathered in diverse ways, including but not limited to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Operating and maintaining our website.</li>\r\n<li>Enhancing, customizing, and expanding our website.</li>\r\n<li>Analyzing your website usage patterns.</li>\r\n<li>Developing new products, services, features, and functionalities.</li>\r\n<li>Communicating with you directly or through partners for customer service, updates, marketing, and promotional purposes.</li>\r\n<li>Sending emails and preventing fraud.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Application of Information as per Privacy Notice:&nbsp;</strong>We may use the information collected as outlined in this Privacy Notice to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Operate, maintain, and enhance the Service and related features.</li>\r\n<li>Provide interest-based ads, push notifications, communications, and offers, considering your precise geolocation.</li>\r\n<li>Facilitate and fulfill orders, including tracking redemption, for Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C vouchers and other goods and services.</li>\r\n<li>Process and confirm bookings with partners and handle payments.</li>\r\n<li>Assess eligibility for offers, products, or services, and evaluate advertising effectiveness.</li>\r\n<li>Address inquiries, respond to requests, perform analytics, and conduct customer research.</li>\r\n<li>Communicate information about Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C and business partners, sometimes by combining data from various sources.</li>\r\n<li>Send reminders, technical notices, updates, security alerts, support messages, marketing content, and requested information.</li>\r\n<li>Administer rewards, surveys, sweepstakes, contests, or promotional activities.</li>\r\n<li>Manage routine business operations, including administration, forum management, fulfillment, analytics, fraud prevention, and compliance with corporate reporting obligations and&nbsp;<a title="Terms of Use" href="https://dealsdrive.app/public/page/2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Terms of Use</a>.</li>\r\n<li>Enable job applications, video posting, or sign-ups for special offers.</li>\r\n<li>Verify requests made under this Privacy Notice.&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Enhance existing information to better understand your interests.</li>\r\n<li>Use your data in accordance with the Card Linked Deals program if you've consented to participate.</li>\r\n<li>Additionally, we may use information with your consent or as required/permitted by law.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Geolocation Usage:</strong>&nbsp;Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C employs your geolocation, including precise details, to deliver location-based offers, products, or services as described in Section 2 above.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Password-Linked Purchases:</strong>&nbsp;For purchases made without a password, we link them to your email address, creating a secure account. If you later create a password, you can view past purchases associated with that email address.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Information Sharing:</strong>&nbsp;If you use Service features to send information about a product or service to another person, we collect their personal information to the extent disclosed by you and may contact them using the provided information.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Legal Basis for Data Processing:</strong>&nbsp;We use your personal data in compliance with the law, typically for contract performance, legitimate interests, legal obligations, or with your consent. Consent is primarily sought for third-party direct marketing communications, and you can withdraw it at any time.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Log Files:</strong>&nbsp;Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C follows standard log file procedures, collecting information such as IP addresses, browser type, ISP, date and time stamp, referring/exit pages, and clicks for analytics. This data is not linked to personally identifiable information and is used for trend analysis, site administration, tracking user movement, and demographic information gathering.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cookies and Web Beacons:</strong>&nbsp;Like other websites, Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C uses cookies to store visitor preferences and track accessed pages. This information optimizes user experience by customizing webpage content based on browser type and other details.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Advertising Partners' Privacy Policies:</strong>&nbsp;Refer to the Privacy Policy of each advertising partner on the provided list for detailed information. Third-party ad servers or networks use technologies like cookies, JavaScript, or Web Beacons to measure advertising campaign effectiveness and personalize content based on users' IP addresses. Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C has no control over these third-party advertisers' cookies.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Third-Party Privacy Policies:</strong>&nbsp;Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C 's Privacy Policy doesn't apply to other advertisers or websites. Consult the respective Privacy Policies of third-party ad servers for more information, including practices and opt-out instructions.</p>\r\n<p><strong>CCPA Privacy Rights:</strong>&nbsp;Under CCPA, California consumers have rights, including accessing, deleting, and opting out of personal data sales. Requests receive a one-month response time. Contact us to exercise these rights.</p>\r\n<p><strong>GDPR Data Protection Rights:</strong>&nbsp;Users have rights, including access, rectification, erasure, processing restriction, objection, and data portability. Requests receive a one-month response time. Contact us to exercise these rights.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Children's Information:</strong>&nbsp;Our priority includes protecting children online. Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C does not knowingly collect Personal Identifiable Information from children under 13. If your child provides such information, contact us for prompt removal from our records.</p>\r\n<p><strong>4. When and Why Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C Shares Information</strong></p>\r\n<p>Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C may disclose your personal information in the following circumstances:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Legal Compliance and Governance:</strong> To comply with the law, legal orders, and government requests, or to support auditing, compliance, and corporate governance functions.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Legal Processes:</strong> In response to a subpoena or similar legal process, including sharing with law enforcement agencies, regulators, and courts in the United Arab Emirates and other countries where operations are conducted.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Vendors provide various services, such as data storage, order fulfillment, email transmission, and digital content management. This sharing is subject to confidentiality obligations consistent with this Privacy Notice and with the condition that service providers use your information solely on our behalf and according to our instructions.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Merchant Collaboration:</strong> With merchants to deliver the services you request, facilitate and fulfill orders, and process and confirm bookings.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Business Transitions:</strong> During business transitions such as mergers, acquisitions, bankruptcy, reorganization, or sale of assets (as outlined in Section 10).</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fraud Protection and Legal Proceedings:</strong> To combat fraud, and criminal activity, and protect our rights, users, and business partners, or as part of legal proceedings affecting Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Affiliate Sharing:</strong> With affiliates and subsidiaries using personal information only for the purposes described in this Privacy Notice.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;With affiliates and subsidiaries using personal information only for the purposes described in this Privacy Notice.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong><span style="text-indent: -18pt;">Consent-based</span>&nbsp;<span style="text-indent: -18pt;">Sharing:</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="WordSection1">\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1.</span><span lang="EN-US">If the information has been aggregated, de-identified, or otherwise does not personally identify you.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2.</span><span lang="EN-US">Otherwise, with your consent.</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US"><strong>Categories of Third Parties:</strong>&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">The personal information may be disclosed to various third- party categories, including:</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C entities</span></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Merchants</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Co-marketers</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Distributors</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Resellers</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Advertising Networks</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Payment Services Providers</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Internet Service Providers</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Data Analytics Providers</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Operating Systems and Platforms</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Social Networks</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Government or Law Enforcement Entities</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Fraud Protection and Prevention Providers</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Delivery Services Providers</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Service Providers</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US"><strong>Categories of Personal Information Disclosed:</strong>&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">For business and operational purposes within the 12 months preceding this Privacy Notice's Effective Date, Deals Drive L.L.C-&nbsp;</span>O.P.C may disclose the following categories of personal information:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Identifiers</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Demographics</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Commercial information</span></li>\r\n<li>Location information</li>\r\n<li>Financial information</li>\r\n<li>Internet and network activity information</li>\r\n<li>Inferences regarding preferences or characteristics</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US"><strong>Data Sharing for Consideration:</strong>&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Certain personal information may be disclosed in exchange for services, insights, or other valuable considerations, involving the same categories mentioned above, and such disclosures have occurred in the 12 months before this Privacy Notice's Effective Date.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US"><strong>Third-Party Data Sharing:</strong>&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C may share your personal data with various parties, including Internal Third Parties, External Third Parties, third parties specified in Section 4 &ndash; How we use your Personal Data above, and third parties to&nbsp;</span>whom we may sell, transfer, or merge parts of our business or assets. If a change occurs in our business, the new owners may use your personal data in line with this Privacy Policy.</li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US"><strong>Security and Processing Instructions:</strong>&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">We mandate that all third parties respect the&nbsp;</span>security of your personal data, treat it in accordance with the law, and process it only for specified purposes and in line with our instructions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">5. Security of Personal Information</span></h3>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C has established a comprehensive information security program that includes administrative, technical, and physical controls to reasonably safeguard personal information. Financial account information is secured using industry-standard encryption</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">technology. However, it's important to note that no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is entirely foolproof. If you have any concerns regarding the security of our website, please don't hesitate to contact us at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@dealsdrive.app">info@dealsdrive.app</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">We have put in place appropriate security measures to prevent accidental loss, unauthorized</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">access, alteration, or disclosure of your personal data. Access to your personal data is limited to employees, agents, contractors, and other third parties with a business need to know. They process your personal data solely based on our instructions and are bound by a duty of confidentiality.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">Procedures are in place to deal with any suspected breaches of personal data, and we will notify you and relevant regulators of any breaches as required by law.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">6. Retention of Personal Data:</span></h3>\r\n<span lang="EN-US">We will keep your personal data for as long as your account is active or as necessary to provide you with our services. If you decide to close your account, we will continue to keep your&nbsp;</span>personal data for as long as it is essential for the effective operation of our business. This includes keeping a record of your transactions for financial reporting or fraud prevention purposes until such purposes cease to exist. Moreover, we will retain your data as required to fulfill legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong><span lang="EN-US">Duration of Personal Data Usage:</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">We will use your personal data only for as long as it is necessary to achieve the purposes for which it was collected. This includes satisfying legal, accounting, or reporting requirements. The appropriate retention period will depend on various factors such as the quantity, nature, and sensitivity of the personal data, potential risks of unauthorized use or disclosure, the purposes of data processing, alternative means to achieve those purposes, and compliance with&nbsp;</span>applicable legal requirements.</p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">Under certain circumstances, we may anonymize your personal data for research or statistical purposes. This will make it unassociated with you. In such cases, this anonymized information may be used indefinitely for these purposes without further notice to you.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">7.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Your Entitlements Concerning Personal Information</span></h3>\r\n<span lang="EN-US">You possess specific rights regarding your personal information:</span>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">You have the right to inquire and request information about the categories and specific pieces of personal information collected about you in the last 12 months. This includes details on the sources of such information, the purpose behind its collection, and the categories of third parties with whom we share it. You also have the right to know if:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">your personal information has been sold or disclosed for business purposes.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">The ability to update your personal information.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">You can request a portable copy of your personal information.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">You have the right to request the deletion of your personal information by Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C, subject to certain exceptions permitted under applicable law.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">The option to opt out of specific disclosures of your personal information for valuable consideration is also a right, and you can exercise this through our &ldquo;Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information&rdquo; tool.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">Exercising any of the mentioned rights does not entitle you to be discriminated against. However, we may provide a different level of service or charge a different rate reasonably related to the value of your personal information.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">In addition to the above, you can update or remove financial account information, and deactivate your Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C account. If you wish to exercise any of the rights set out above, please contact us at:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@dealsdrive.app">info@dealsdrive.app</a></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">Under specific circumstances, data protection laws grant you the following rights (refer to Section 8 &ndash; Glossary below):</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Request access to your personal data.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Request correction of your personal data.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Request erasure of your personal data.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Object to the processing of your personal data.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Request restriction of processing your personal data.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Request the transfer of your personal data.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">The right to withdraw consent.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">To exercise any of the rights mentioned above, please contact us at&nbsp;<a title="info@dealsdrive.app" href="mailto:info@dealsdrive.app">info@dealsdrive.app</a></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">8. Your Rights and Choices and Legal Rights Under Data Protection Laws:</span></h3>\r\nAt Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C, we believe in providing you with a personalized experience tailored to your preferences. While we strive to enhance your experience by understanding your interests, we acknowledge your right to control the information you share with us and the communications you receive. Here are key aspects of your rights and choices:\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong><span lang="EN-US">Access and Information</span></strong><span lang="EN-US"><strong>:</strong> You have the right to know about the personal information collected over the past 12 months, including specific details, sources, purposes, and&nbsp;</span>disclosures to third parties. This transparency extends to understanding if your data has been sold for business purposes.</li>\r\n<li><strong><span lang="EN-US">Updates and Corrections</span></strong><span lang="EN-US"><strong>:</strong> Your personal information must be accurate. You can update your information to ensure it reflects the latest details.</span></li>\r\n<li><strong><span lang="EN-US">Portability</span></strong><span lang="EN-US"><strong>:</strong> Request a portable copy of your personal information for your records.</span></li>\r\n<li><strong><span lang="EN-US">Deletion Requests</span></strong><span lang="EN-US"><strong>:</strong> You can request the deletion of your personal information, with certain exceptions mandated by applicable law.</span></li>\r\n<li><strong><span lang="EN-US">Opt-Out of Disclosures</span></strong><span lang="EN-US"><strong>:</strong> Opt-out of certain disclosures of your personal information for valuable consideration using our "Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information" tool.</span></li>\r\n<li><strong><span lang="EN-US">Non-Discrimination</span></strong><span lang="EN-US"><strong>:</strong> We respect your choices. You will not face discrimination for&nbsp;</span>exercising your rights, although different service levels may apply based on the value of your personal information.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">In addition to these choices, you can manage your communication preferences and deactivate your Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C account at any time.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">Beyond operational choices, you have legal rights safeguarded by data protection laws:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong><span lang="EN-US">Access Request</span></strong><span lang="EN-US"><strong>:</strong> Obtain a copy of the personal data we hold and ensure lawful processing.</span></li>\r\n<li><strong>Correction</strong><span lang="EN-US"><strong>:</strong> Rectify incomplete or inaccurate data, ensuring its accuracy.</span></li>\r\n<li><strong>Erasure</strong><span lang="EN-US"><strong>:</strong> Request the deletion or removal of personal data under specific circumstances.</span></li>\r\n<li><strong>Objection to Processing</strong><span lang="EN-US"><strong>:</strong> Object to processing based on legitimate interests or for direct marketing purposes.</span></li>\r\n<li><strong>Restriction of Processing</strong><span lang="EN-US"><strong>:</strong> Suspend data processing in certain scenarios, including verifying data accuracy or addressing legal claims.</span></li>\r\n<li><strong>Data Transfer</strong><span lang="EN-US"><strong>:</strong> Request the transfer of your personal data in a machine-readable format.</span></li>\r\n<li><strong>Consent Withdrawal</strong><span lang="EN-US"><strong>:</strong> Withdraw consent at any time without affecting prior lawful processing.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">Your privacy is crucial to us. Should you wish to exercise any of these rights or have further inquiries, please get in touch with us at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@dealsdrive.app">info@dealsdrive.app</a></span></p>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">9.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Privacy Practices of Third Parties</span></h3>\r\n<span lang="EN-US">It is important to note that this Privacy Notice specifically addresses how Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C handles and shares information during your use of the Service. Other websites accessible through links from the Service, as well as our co-branded websites, may have their own privacy policies outlining their practices for collecting, using, and disclosing personal information.</span>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">Additionally, our business partners may have their own privacy policies. We strongly&nbsp;</span>recommend that you carefully review the privacy notices provided by these external entities before sharing any personal information or participating in sponsored offers or promotions.</p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">By consenting to this Privacy Policy, you acknowledge and authorize the sharing of your n</span>personal data, such as your name, email address, gender, date of birth, and nationality, with third parties for marketing purposes. These third parties are bound by their own privacy policies, which apply when they collect information about you. However, they may provide you with options to opt out of having your information collected or used in this way. Bottom of Form</p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">You have the choice to request us or third parties to cease sending you marketing messages at any time. You can accomplish this by accessing the website and adjusting your marketing preferences through the relevant checkboxes. Alternatively, you may use the opt-out links provided in any marketing message sent to you or reach out to us directly.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">It's important to note that opting out of marketing messages will not impact any personal data you have provided to us through product or service purchases, warranty registrations, product or service experiences, or other transactions.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">10.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Modification Of Purpose, Business Transfers, and Corporate Changes</span></h3>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C has the right to share, transfer, or authorize any information related to the Service, including Personal Information, to a future owner, co-owner, or operator of the&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Service or any of its components. Moreover, Deal Drisve L.L.C- O.P.C may disclose such&nbsp;</span>information in association with a corporate merger, consolidation, or restructuring, the sale of all or a part of the company's stock and assets, or any other corporate change, including, but not limited to, any due diligence process.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">We will only use your personal data for the specific purposes for which we originally collected it unless we determine that we need to use it for a different reason that aligns with the original purpose. If we need to use your data for a new purpose, we will explain how it aligns with the&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">original purpose upon request. If we ever need to use your personal data for an unrelated purpose, we will inform you and provide an explanation of the legal basis that allows us to do so. Please note that there may be times when we are required or permitted by law to process your data without your knowledge or consent, but we will always do so in compliance with the rules mentioned above.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">11.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Cookies and Tracking Technologies</span></h3>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">You have the option to configure your browser settings to either reject all cookies, accept only certain cookies, or receive notifications when a website attempts to set or access cookies.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">However, it's important to note that disabling or rejecting cookies may result in certain parts of our websites being unavailable or functioning incorrectly. For more details about the cookies utilized, please refer to Section 2 - How We Collect Your Personal Data, located above.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">We and our partners employ various technologies, including cookies, pixels, and web beacons, to collect and store information when you use this website. Web beacons track specific&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">behaviors such as email delivery, openings, and link clicks. They enable us to gather details like your IP address, browser, email client type, and similar information. Additionally, they assist in tracking website usage and traffic. Reports are generated when we send emails to you, allowing us to collect and analyze relevant information. These cookies are stored on your hard drive but do not read its contents; they enable our website to recognize you upon your return. If you are on our mailing list and wish to be removed, please use the "Contact Us" section to submit your request. If there is no unsubscribe button, kindly contact us to facilitate your removal.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">12.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Navigation and Clickstream Data</span></h3>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">As you navigate through our website, we collect data on the pages you visit, the features you use, and how long you spend on each page. This information is collected anonymously and&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">cannot be linked to your personal identity. We use this data to provide support and analyze your purchases, improve your website experience, comply with legal requirements, and deliver specialized advertising content and recommendations. The information may be shared with our staff and third-party providers involved in completing your transaction, delivering your order, and supporting your use of the website.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">13.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Minors' Privacy Protection</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">The Service is crafted for a broad audience and is not designed for individuals under the age of&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">16. Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C has no verified knowledge of the sale of information pertaining to minors under 16 years of age.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">By using Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C, you confirm that you are at least 16 years old and recognize that creating an account and completing purchases through the Service necessitates a minimum age of 18.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">The Site and the Service are not aimed at individuals under the age of 16, and we do not knowingly gather or request information from anyone below this age. Additionally, the Site prohibits individuals under the age of 16 from registering for the Service. Should we discover that personal information has inadvertently been collected from someone under the age of 16 without the consent of a parent or guardian, we will promptly delete such information. If you suspect that we have collected information from an individual under 16, please contact us at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@dealsdrive.app">info@dealsdrive.app</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">Our websites and mobile applications are not tailored for children under the age of sixteen (16), and we do not promote our products or services to such children. We do not knowingly collect any data from children under the age of 16. Furthermore, our products and services are not&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">accessible to individuals who are not of legal age to enter into a fully enforceable contract; an individual must be at least 18 years of age to engage in such transactions.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">14.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">General Data Protection Rights GDPR</span></h3>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">We want to ensure that you are fully aware of your GDPR data protection rights. As a user, you have the following entitlements:</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">The right to access - You can request copies of your personal data. However, we may charge a small fee for this service.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">The right to rectification - You can request us to correct any information that you believe is inaccurate. Additionally, you have the right to request us to complete any incomplete&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">information.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">The right to erasure - You can request us to erase your personal data under certain conditions.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">The right to restrict processing - You can request us to restrict the processing of your personal data under certain conditions.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">The right to object to processing - You can object to our processing of your personal data under certain conditions.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">6.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">The right to data portability - You can request us to transfer the data that we have collected to another organization, or directly to you, under certain conditions.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">If you make a request, we have one month to respond to you. If you want to exercise any of these rights, please contact us.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">15.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Protection of Your Personal Information</span></h3>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">Our website has secure pages that collect user information, and any critical data is stored in encrypted form. We employ various technical and management practices to safeguard the confidentiality, security, and integrity of all data stored on our system. Our servers are equipped with Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) and encryption technology that is compatible with popular web browsers such as Netscape Navigator, Microsoft Internet Explorer, Firefox, Safari, and Chrome.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">16.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Modifications To This Privacy Policy</span></h3>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">This Privacy Policy may undergo periodic updates to align with our business operations and legal obligations. In the event of any revisions to our Privacy Policy, the updated version will be published on this webpage and within the privacy sections of any pertinent platforms.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">17.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Verifying, updating, and amending personal information</span></h3>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">To verify, update, or modify your personal information on our app, please log in to your account and select "My Account". From there, you can access "Account Info" and "Saved Address" to update any information as needed.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">18.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Information about the Services We Offer</span></h3>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">We strive to provide you with the best service possible and to achieve this, we may periodically send you information about our products, services, discounts, promotions, and campaigns that we believe may interest you. We will only send you marketing communications if you have given us your consent. If you no longer wish to receive these details and would like to unsubscribe&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">from marketing communications, you can contact us via email or change your relevant settings by logging into your account and clicking the "my account" link on the user main page.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">19.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">How to Delete Your Account</span></h3>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">At Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C, you have the option to delete your account using our mobile application. However, please note that if there are any pending transactions or outstanding amounts due, you will not be able to delete your account. Before deleting your account, you must complete all pending transactions and/or payments.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">To delete your account through our mobile application, please follow these simple steps:</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Open the Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C mobile app on your device.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Go to the 'settings' menu, which is usually located within your user profile section.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Select 'Account Info.'</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Click on the 'delete your account' option.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Follow the on-screen instructions to confirm and complete the deletion process.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">Please keep in mind that when you delete your account, your personal data will also be deleted.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">However, we may be required to keep some of your information if we process it as part of our legal obligations, or in pursuit of our own (or a third party&rsquo;s legitimate interests) such as the&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">assertion of, or defense against, legal claims, preventing fraud or protecting ourselves or others against abusive behavior. Once your data is deleted from the mobile app, it will be permanently removed from our systems and cannot be recovered. If you have any questions, please contact our customer support.</span></p>\r\n<h4><span lang="EN-US">20. Entire Agreement. </span></h4>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">This Agreement, our Terms of Use, Terms of Sale, Rules of Use, Terms of reservation, End-user Licence agreement, and our Privacy Policy constitute the entire agreement between you and Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C with respect to the Application and supersede all prior or contemporaneous understandings and agreements, whether written or oral, with respect to the Application.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span lang="EN-US">21.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Contact Us</span></h3>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top: 9.2pt; line-height: 107%;"><span lang="EN-US">Please contact us if you have any questions or comments about our privacy practices or this Privacy Notice. You can reach us online at&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US"><a href="mailto:info@dealsdrive.app">info@dealsdrive.app</a></span></p>		\N	\N	\N	2024-03-30 05:13:26	2024-04-01 07:07:15	REFUND_POLICY
8	Rules of use		1	<div class="WordSection1">\r\n<p align="center"><strong><span lang="EN-US">Rules of Use Deals Drive L.L.C- O.P.C</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoTitle" style="margin-top: 9.3pt;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><span lang="EN-US">Effective as of: March First, 2024</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: .1pt 0cm .0001pt 0cm;">Welcome to the world of Deals Drive LL, where carefully curated deals and offers are tailored to meet your needs, ensuring the application's goal of providing you with the best offers and achieving optimal savings percentages.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: .1pt 0cm .0001pt 0cm;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: .1pt 0cm .0001pt 0cm;"><strong><span style="text-indent: 0cm;">Deals</span> <span style="text-indent: 0cm;">Drive</span> <span style="text-indent: 0cm;">Deals</span> <span style="text-indent: 0cm;">are:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: .1pt 0cm .0001pt 0cm;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: .1pt 0cm .0001pt 0cm;"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1. Vouchers are available 24/7 unless otherwise stated in the terms of a particular deal.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: .1pt 0cm .0001pt 0cm;"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2. Redemption can be made by a single individual or any number of people in a group.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: .1pt 0cm .0001pt 0cm;"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3. Some Vouchers are limited to the number of people, for example (up to one offer for two people, two offers for four people, and three offers for six people or&nbsp;</span>more)</p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: .1pt 0cm .0001pt 0cm;"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4. Before requesting the service, notify the merchant of the Voucher and confirm its acceptance.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: .1pt 0cm .0001pt 0cm;"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 5. The voucher must be presented before payment or when requesting the invoice.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: .1pt 0cm .0001pt 0cm;"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 6. Vouchers are not valid when combined with other discount offers, promotions, special menu items, or loyalty/rewards programs.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: .1pt 0cm .0001pt 0cm;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 7. We disclaim any responsibility if an outlet is temporarily or permanently closed during the validity period of the offer.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: .1pt 0cm .0001pt 0cm;"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 8. In the event of a dispute, the invoice must be settled in accordance with local laws. We will contact the concerned parties to resolve the issue.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: .1pt 0cm .0001pt 0cm;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: .1pt 0cm .0001pt 0cm;"><strong><span lang="EN-US">1.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Rules of Use for Deals Drive Deals:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">The utilization of all Deals Drive Deals is governed by the following Rules of Use, in addition to any terms of use provided with the Deals. Customers are advised to carefully review&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">these Rules before availing any deal.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: .05pt 0cm .0001pt 23.0pt;"><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="text-indent: -18.25pt;">1.1<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp; </span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="text-indent: -18.25pt;">Deal Validity:</span></strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span lang="EN-US">Your subscription is valid for 12 months from the date of your subscription, unless otherwise specified.</span></li>\r\n<li>Vouchers remain valid for 24 hours after acquisition unless explicitly stated otherwise.</li>\r\n<li>Deals can only be redeemed through the service provider that issued them.</li>\r\n<li>Deals apply solely to the specified items/services and designated location(s) as outlined in the deal.</li>\r\n<li>Exclusively designed, deals cannot be combined with other discount offers, promotions, special deals, or rewards programs.</li>\r\n<li>In the event of a service provider refusing to honor a Deal, please reach out to Deals Drive Customer Service at <span lang="EN-US"><a href="mailto:info@dealsdrive.app">info@dealsdrive.app</a></span><span lang="EN-US">.</span></li>\r\n<li>Offers do not apply to any additional service charges or taxes.</li>\r\n<li>Offers are valid seven days a week unless specified on the Offer.</li>\r\n<li>Offers are not redeemable for cash unless required by law.</li>\r\n<li>Unauthorized reproduction, resale, or modification of any Offer is strictly prohibited. Offers become invalid if they are resold or exchanged.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="WordSection2">\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US"><strong style="text-indent: -24px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="text-indent: -18.3pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1.2<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="text-indent: -18.3pt;">Redeeming<span style="letter-spacing: -.7pt;">&nbsp;</span>Offers</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 9.25pt 0cm .0001pt 5.0pt;"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span lang="EN-US">Claiming offers on your app is a simple process:</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Choose the desired offer you wish to benefit from on the application.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Click on the "Get Deal" button.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Watch a brief promotional advertisement lasting 15 to 30 seconds.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Upon completing the ad, you will receive a QR code.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 5.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Present the QR code to the server before settling the bill.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 6.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Upon entering or scanning the QR code, the offer will be redeemed, and the corresponding item or service will be deducted from your bill.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 7.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">To redeem more offers, simply repeat the same process.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 8.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">The number of offers that can be used at the same visit varies from one merchant to another (please review the terms of use for each merchant).</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 9. For added convenience, acquire the voucher before your visit to mitigate any potential technical issues at the service location (the voucher remains valid for 24 hours from the time of acquisition).</p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left: 0cm;"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>1.3<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp; </span></strong></span><strong><span lang="EN-US">Types of Offers Offered.</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="line-height: 107%; margin: 9.1pt 0cm .0001pt 23.0pt;"><span lang="EN-US">Our app is designed to offer a diverse range of deals catering to all categories. These deals come in various forms:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-top: 7.95pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: 41.05pt;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span><span lang="EN-US">1.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Percentage Discounts:</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Enjoy percentage discounts on the full value of the provided service. The discount percentage varies, ranging from 10% to 60% and more.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Buy one get one free:</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Explore the "Buy One Get One Free" offers across a wide spectrum of services, including restaurants, hotels, entertainment, fashion stores, and more.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">Service Bundles:</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="WordSection3">\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="line-height: 107%; margin: 2.0pt 0cm .0001pt 5.0pt;"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span lang="EN-US">Avail offers where purchasing one service entitles you to receive another service for free. This category encompasses service providers in areas such as barbershops, beauty and skincare centers, car care, beauty and dental clinics, daily services, and more.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="line-height: 107%; margin: 2.0pt 0cm .0001pt 5.0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="line-height: 107%; margin: 2.0pt 0cm .0001pt 5.0pt;"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong> &nbsp;1.4<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp; </span></strong></span><strong><span lang="EN-US">How Do Offers Work?</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-top: 2.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: 41.05pt;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US"> &nbsp; a)</span><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">If The Offer Is a Percentage-Based Discount:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-top: 2.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: 41.05pt;"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;the specified percentage will be deducted from the total amount of the bill.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: 41.05pt; margin: 2.15pt 332.1pt .0001pt 5.0pt;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang="EN-US">b)</span><s